---
import "@styles/global.module.css";
export const name = "Water Bills mod release";
export const description = "A new mod by Akatsuki2555 was released. Water Bills.";
export const date = "2024-04-28";

import Header from "@components/header.astro";
import Footer from "@components/footer.astro";
import Meta from "@components/meta.astro";
import Cursor from "@components/cursor.astro";
import Scripts from "@components/scripts.astro";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <Meta
            name="Water Bills mod release"
            description="The Water Bills mod enhances My Summer Car gameplay by adding realistic water management. Players receive water bills alongside electricity and phone bills, adjusting water price and consumption for immersive gameplay. Fairness is ensured as prices can't be changed mid-game. Install now for authentic water management experience."
            
        />
        <Scripts />
        <Cursor />
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <h1>Enhance Your My Summer Car Experience with Water Bills Mod</h1>

            <p>
                Are you looking to elevate your My Summer Car gameplay to a
                whole new level of realism and immersion? Look no further than
                the <a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/mysummercar/mods/5475"
                    >Water Bills mod</a
                >! Designed to seamlessly integrate with your gaming experience,
                this mod introduces a crucial aspect often overlooked in
                simulation games: managing water consumption and bills.
            </p>

            <p>
                With the Water Bills mod, players can now expect to receive
                water bills alongside her electricity and phone bills. Gone are
                the days of unrealistic unlimited water usageâ€”now, you'll have
                to keep an eye on your virtual water consumption just like you
                would in real life.
            </p>

            <p>
                But that's not all. This mod comes packed with features to
                customize your water usage experience. You can adjust the price
                per liter of water to suit your virtual budget, ensuring that
                every drop counts. Plus, with adjustable water consumption
                settings for both bathroom showers and kitchen taps, you have
                full control over your virtual water usage habits.
            </p>

            <p>
                One of the best parts? The mod is designed with fairness in
                mind. Once the game starts, prices can't be tampered with to
                prevent cheating the system. This ensures a level playing field
                for all players, making for a more engaging and authentic
                gameplay experience.
            </p>

            <p>
                So, why wait? Install the <a
                    href="https://www.nexusmods.com/mysummercar/mods/5475"
                    >Water Bills mod</a
                > today and immerse yourself in a world where every drop of water
                matters. Take your My Summer Car adventures to the next level and
                discover the joy of realistic water management.
            </p>

            <p>
                This mod is owned by <a href="https://akatsuki.nekoweb.org/"
                    >Akatsuki2555</a
                >, the creator of many other mods and projects. You can find the
                source code of this mod on <a
                    href="http://codeberg.org/Akatsuki/WaterBills"
                    >http://codeberg.org/Akatsuki/WaterBills</a
                >.
            </p>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>
